    </div>
    <div style="background: #fefce8; border-left: 4px solid #eab308; padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
      <strong>Step 3: Vocabulary Mining</strong>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0;">Add 5–10 useful new words to your flashcard deck with the drama scene as context.</p>
    </div>
